TASK WAS: Create a RemoteEvent in ReplicatedStorage to communicate car movement from the client to the server.
SUCCESSFUL COMMANDS EXECUTED:
[
  {
    "type": "create_instance",
    "payload": {
      "className": "RemoteEvent",
      "parent": "ReplicatedStorage",
      "name": "CarMovementEvent",
      "properties": {}
    }
  }
]

TASK WAS: Write a ServerScriptService script to receive car movement commands from clients and apply them to the car model.
SUCCESSFUL COMMANDS EXECUTED:
[
  {
    "type": "insert_script",
    "payload": {
      "className": "Script",
      "parent": "ServerScriptService",
      "name": "CarMovementController",
      "source": "local ReplicatedStorage = game:GetService(\"ReplicatedStorage\")\nlocal CarMovementEvent = ReplicatedStorage:WaitForChild(\"CarMovementEvent\")\n\nCarMovementEvent.OnServerEvent:Connect(function(player, direction, speed)\n    local character = player.Character\n    if character then\n        local primaryPart = character.PrimaryPart\n        if primaryPart then\n            primaryPart.Velocity = primaryPart.Velocity + (direction * speed)\n        end\n    end\nend)\n"
    }
  }
]
